## 💫 Demo

## 🚀 Quick start

1.  **Install dependencies.**

    ```shell
    yarn
    ```

1.  **Start developing.**

    ```shell
    yarn start
    ```
    Your site is now running at `http://localhost:8000`!

2.  **Build production.**

    ```shell
    yarn build
    ```
